    "_criteria": "Value = raw mention count across the full PDF text using primary name + synonym list from the technique taxonomy. A technique is considered triggered when raw frequency ≥ 2; mentions ≥ 1 but below threshold appear in the 'Add by occurrence' dropdown so the reviewer can promote them manually. Per analytical_techniques_proposal.md, a threshold of ≥ 2 better distinguishes papers that genuinely apply a technique from those that cite it in passing.",
